5) HIGH-LEVEL ARCHITECTURE
============================================================
Frontend (React) calls FastAPI API.
FastAPI coordinates:
- Auth + RBAC
- File ingestion and secure storage
- Parsing/OCR/QR extraction
- Detection + sanitization
- Risk aggregation
- Audit logging/export
- Backup export

Core data stores:
- Database tables: users, files, audit_logs
- Encrypted originals on disk: secure_storage/originals/*.enc

