18) CONFIGURATION (.env)
============================================================
Template path:
- backend/.env.example

Critical keys:
- DATABASE_URL
- JWT_SECRET_KEY
- FILE_MASTER_KEY (preferred)
- CORS_ALLOW_ORIGINS
- MAX_UPLOAD_MB
- STEPUP_REQUIRED_FOR_RAW_DOWNLOAD
- BACKUP_STEPUP_REQUIRED
- OCR_LANGS / OCR_TESS_LANGS
- VIRUSTOTAL_ENABLED / VIRUSTOTAL_API_KEY

Recommendation:
- In production, store secrets in secret manager, not plain .env.

============================================================
19) LOCAL RUN STEPS
============================================================
Backend:
1. cd pii-guardian/backend
2. python -m venv venv
3. venv\Scripts\activate
4. pip install -r requirements.txt
5. copy .env.example .env
6. python main.py

Frontend:
1. cd pii-guardian/frontend/frontend
2. npm install
3. npm run dev

