============================================================
21) CURRENT LIMITATIONS AND NEXT IMPROVEMENTS
============================================================
Limitations:
- VirusTotal hash reputation may miss brand-new threats.
- OCR accuracy depends on scan quality and language fonts.
- Local disk encrypted storage is suitable for prototype/small deployment.

High-impact roadmap:
- S3 + KMS backend for encrypted originals at scale
- Hybrid malware scanning (VT + sandbox/ClamAV)
- Queued async processing for very large documents
- DLP policy templates and approval workflow
- SIEM webhook streaming and alert rules

